      "date": "2012-11-28 18:15:20.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAndreas, this change should only affect you if all of the following are true.\n\n- you are running Zol earlier than 0.6.0-rc11 (tagged on September 18, 2012)\n- you use the lustre init script to start services\n- the zfs pool devices are imported from /dev/mapper or /dev/disk/by-vdev, and\n- you aren't setting ZPOOL_IMPORT_DIR in /etc/sysconfig/lustre",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
